data.description: A jewel in Cedar Key! No storm related issues of any kind.  Live in downtown Cedar Key in this beautiful updated home that has charm and great options for a business to boot!  Ideally located to walk, shop in Cedar Key and enjoy the public garden right next door. The park and beach are just around the corner. Land use rules allow many different options for business, cafe, retail, professional office, live here/work here--options are endless. This home is high and dry with no flooding from recent storm and has been updated with paint inside and out, painted floors, soaking tub and shower added in bathroom, back deck is a bonus that has cozy space to relax during all seasons of the year. Front screened porch is a wonderful place to enjoy the view of City. Purchase the existing golf cart business (sold separately) or have rental income from leasing an area on the property. This is the semi-retirement package you need, a ready made business and home all in one. Come live island style and earn an easy income while absorbing that Florida sunshine!
